      "date": "2020-04-27 01:13:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis new macro is (almost?) exclusive used to test an existing nid.\n\nI think it might be nicer to create an inline that tests if a given nid is on the loop-back net.  is_lonet(nid) ???\nThe transition to IPv6 will make nids bigger and using == for comparison isn't so convenient.  So I've rather avoid it now if possible.",
