          {
            "commit": "56203e4ba0a64789e42ea45946e8c51f1db351fb",
            "subject": "LU-12222 lnet: Introduce constant for the lolnd NID"
          }
        ],
        "author": {
          "name": "Chris Horn",
          "email": "hornc@cray.com",
          "date": "2020-04-22 16:42:27.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Oleg Drokin",
          "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2020-05-07 05:42:59.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-12222 lnet: Primary NID of lolnd NID is the lolnd NID",
        "message": "LU-12222 lnet: Primary NID of lolnd NID is the lolnd NID\n\nWe want Lustre traffic that is intended for the local peer to be sent\nand received over the lolnd. The function ptlrpc_uuid_to_peer() will\ncurrently resolve a NID to the lolnd NID, but ptlrpc_connection_get()\nwill overwrite this selection with the result from LNetPrimaryNID().\n\nHave LNetPrimaryNID return the lolnd NID when it is passed the lolnd\nNID.\n\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-8457\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <hornc@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I02708bb45f8440091782ca7886bac7656efb0223\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/38313\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
  "requirements": [],
  "submit_records": []
